The Rover;;2014;;R;;Action,Crime,Drama;;6.4;;David Michôd;;Guy Pearce,Robert Pattinson,Scoot McNairy,David Field,Chan Kien,Tek Kong Lim,Tawanda Manyimo,Scott Perry,Richard Green,Ben Armer,Ethan Hanslow,Gillian Jones,Jamie Fallon,Frank C. Sun,Samuel F. Lee,Susan Prior,Gerald Coulthard,Christina Ling;;Ten years after a global economic collapse, a cold-blooded drifter traverses the scorched Australian outback on a mission to track down the men who stole his last remaining possession - his car. When he crosses paths with a badly wounded member of the gang, he takes the vulnerable, naïve young man along as his unwitting accomplice.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt2345737/